{"title":"一步步来：打造您自己的SFTP服务器","slug":"一步步来：打造您自己的SFTP服务器","date":"2024-03-23T00:18:41.000Z","updated":"2024-03-23T00:30:02.740Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/一步步来：打造您自己的SFTP服务器.json","excerpt":"使用sftpgo搭建sftp服务器，以实现文件共享及权限控制。","covers":["/2024/03/23/yi-bu-bu-lai-da-zao-nin-zi-ji-de-sftp-fu-wu-qi/2024-03-23_082750.jpg"],"content":"<p>使用sftpgo搭建sftp服务器，以实现文件共享及权限控制。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>之前有用过其它文件共享的软件，忘记了具体是哪个了，这次就记录下来。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"项目地址及简介\"><a href=\"#项目地址及简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"项目地址及简介\"></a>项目地址及简介</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/drakkan/sftpgo\">SFTPGo</a></p>\n<p>Fully featured and highly configurable SFTP server with optional HTTP&#x2F;S, FTP&#x2F;S and WebDAV support. Several storage backends are supported: local filesystem, encrypted local filesystem, S3 (compatible) Object Storage, Google Cloud Storage, Azure Blob Storage, SFTP. </p>\n<h2 id=\"安装及启动\"><a href=\"#安装及启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装及启动\"></a>安装及启动</h2><p>这里是windows下，默认安装到了windows服务，安装完成之后，修改默认配置：</p>\n<p>配置文件路径：C:\\ProgramData\\SFTPGo\\sftpgo.json，</p>\n<p>调整管理界面的端口号：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"httpd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"bindings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"port\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">9999</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>sftp默认端口号2022,可在配置文件中调整</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"sftpd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"bindings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"port\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2022</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"apply_proxy_config\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>之后在windows服务中启动即可:</p>\n<p>管理地址：<a href=\"http://localhost:9999/web/admin\">http://localhost:9999/web/admin</a> 可用来配置用户及权限：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2024/03/23/yi-bu-bu-lai-da-zao-nin-zi-ji-de-sftp-fu-wu-qi/2024-03-23_082750.jpg\"></p>\n<p>最后使用SFTP客户端如winscp连接即可。</p>\n","more":"<blockquote>\n<p>之前有用过其它文件共享的软件，忘记了具体是哪个了，这次就记录下来。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"项目地址及简介\"><a href=\"#项目地址及简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"项目地址及简介\"></a>项目地址及简介</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/drakkan/sftpgo\">SFTPGo</a></p>\n<p>Fully featured and highly configurable SFTP server with optional HTTP&#x2F;S, FTP&#x2F;S and WebDAV support. Several storage backends are supported: local filesystem, encrypted local filesystem, S3 (compatible) Object Storage, Google Cloud Storage, Azure Blob Storage, SFTP. </p>\n<h2 id=\"安装及启动\"><a href=\"#安装及启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装及启动\"></a>安装及启动</h2><p>这里是windows下，默认安装到了windows服务，安装完成之后，修改默认配置：</p>\n<p>配置文件路径：C:\\ProgramData\\SFTPGo\\sftpgo.json，</p>\n<p>调整管理界面的端口号：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"httpd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"bindings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"port\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">9999</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>sftp默认端口号2022,可在配置文件中调整</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"sftpd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"bindings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"port\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2022</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"apply_proxy_config\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>之后在windows服务中启动即可:</p>\n<p>管理地址：<a href=\"http://localhost:9999/web/admin\">http://localhost:9999/web/admin</a> 可用来配置用户及权限：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2024/03/23/yi-bu-bu-lai-da-zao-nin-zi-ji-de-sftp-fu-wu-qi/2024-03-23_082750.jpg\"></p>\n<p>最后使用SFTP客户端如winscp连接即可。</p>","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"运维","path":"api/tags/运维.json"}]}